data.description: Great location! This spacious and charming older home is perfectly situated in a convenient location. With generous living spaces and a touch of vintage character, this residence offers a unique blend of comfort and nostalgia. Lots of storage! Delightful sunroom porch, providing the perfect blend of indoor comfort and outdoor serenity. Large dining room has lots of elbow room for entertaining. Living room has fireplace with shelving on both sides. Newer flooring and interior paint. Detached garage has access from the alley. Full home inspection has been completed. Welcome home!
